ygData.subject: Names for Characters
ygData.msgSnippet: hello everyone, i just want to share this information, because some may have problems with naming their characters: the following link is a Fantasy Name
ygData.messageBody:
hello everyone,

i just want to share this information, because some may have problems with naming their characters:

the following link is a "Fantasy Name Generator" (this one was new to
me):

http://spitfire.ausys.se/johan/names/default.htm


i used the following one for some of my (16) chars, because you can
get real name and also get to know the meaning of the name:

http://womencentral.msn.com/babies/tools/namer.asp

on the babyname site, there are also some other links, to search for the meaning of a name, and much more ...
especially ads :-( ...


- bilt

--
Biltilie Dwimmerlaik
level 54 female gnome magician
Tarew Marr
